    <item>
      <title>Publisher-Subscriber Pattern</title>
      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-engineering/design-and-architecture/architecture-styles-and-patterns/architecture-styles/messaging-oriented/event-driven-architecture/publish-subscribe/publisher-subscriber-pattern/</link>
